{"questionId":"a22baf87-f61e-43f7-b868-52cf0e05d234_13","correctAnswer":"89","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Set up","content":"Circumference formula: $C = \\pi d$. Substitute $C = 89\\pi$: $89\\pi = \\pi d$."},{"title":"Solve","content":"Divide both sides by $\\pi$: $d = 89$."},{"title":"Answer","content":"<strong>89</strong> is correct."}]}